components:
  schemas:
    Comment:
      type: object
      properties:
        _id:
          type: string
          readOnly: true
          title: ' id'
        message:

          maxLength: 256
        userId:

          maxLength: 100
        name:

          maxLength: 256
        avatar:
          type: string
          maxLength: 256
        time:
          type: integer
      required:
      - _id
    Room:
      type: object
      properties:
        _id:
          type: string
          readOnly: true
          title: ' id'
        room_name:
          type: string
          maxLength: 100
        description:
          type: string
          maxLength: 300
        private:
          type: boolean
          default: false
        room_url:
          type: string
          maxLength: 300
        memberId:

          items:
            type: string
            maxLength: 128
          default: []
      required:
      - _id
  securitySchemes:
    cookieAuth:
      type: apiKey
      in: cookie
      name: sessionid
